    "(?i)(?:(?:low[- ]trust|untrusted)\\s+source\\s+(?:upranked|elevated|outranks)|(?:fake|spoofed|synthetic)\\s+(?:weight|priority|authority)\\s+(?:tag|field|score)\\s+(?:on|for)\\s+(?:source|evidence))"
